    <item>
      <title>Meta 因转向人工智能而关闭增强现实工作室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/meta-shuttering-augmented-reality-studio-amid-pivot-to-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 将关闭一家增强现实工作室，优先投资其他领域，包括蓬勃发展的人工智能业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/meta-shuttering-augmented-reality-studio-amid-pivot-to-ai</guid>
